---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 545
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=The Safeguarding of Prayer
By: Swami Ramdas
---
Some hours of the day (should be) set apart for meditation so that the
work in which we would be engaged during the other hours may be done
as a spontaneous and blissful outflow of the Eternal Reality dwelling
within us.
